verbose_text: Specifically, miR-8 facilitates adipogenesis by targeting Wntless and CG32767, while miR-344 has been shown to inhibit the adipocytic differentiation of 3T3-L1 cells by targeting glycogen synthase kinase-3beta (GSK3beta).
